{"tid":2235421,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"參考xx同xx 發明咗支懶人牙刷","createTime":"2020-10-08T16:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T15:17:53.000Z","uid":319228,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"136e943a538cf30c481265623c69416c0c218971","tid":2235421,"uid":319228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T16:11:11.000Z","msg":"就算電動牙刷 都要用手拎住<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔夠快<br />\n<br />\n所以我參考咗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jVgpKhC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjVgpKhC.jpg&h=2620c457&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z5vBApi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ5vBApi.png&h=cc65631d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再利用聲波振動牙刷嘅原理<br />\n<br />\n發明咗個唔洗用手拎 又可以一次過擦晒咁多隻牙嘅牙擦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K5O7G55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK5O7G55.jpg&h=d72294bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Me74KjC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMe74KjC.jpg&h=40268f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nWRtrzr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnWRtrzr.gif&h=e82cb1f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n計番條數<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n普通牙刷 每次刷牙時間：2分鐘x 60= 120秒<br />\n<br />\n一般成人牙齒數量：12隻門牙+16隻大牙= 28隻<br />\n<br />\n牙齒表面：（12+16)x2 + 16= 72面<br />\n<br />\n每個擦牙動作周期所覆蓋牙齒表面：2面<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以每隻牙要用嘅時間係：<br />\n120&divide;(72/2)<br />\n≌3.33秒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n換言之 用呢支牙刷只需3.33秒就可以擦完一次牙<br />\n<br />\n每次擦牙就可以慳返接近117秒"},{"pid":"288b06613ad76f9a5a16b5fa30cc045a07ec8330","tid":2235421,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T16:12:09.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"0b98eca7830a9eeb906f2c55f99c9995e5110705","tid":2235421,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T16:38:20.000Z","msg":"睇完之後我淨係知道<br />\n樓豬完全冇智慧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n齒"},{"pid":"8448f05349d8989e7a419daef4d51c46c5ac7226","tid":2235421,"uid":186177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T16:41:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://y-brush.com/en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fy-brush.com%2Fen&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr8jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=072b4ba3\" target=\"_blank\">https://y-brush.com/en</a><br />\n樓豬又抄"},{"pid":"89939ada85ab88a5e11cd347bad5e2c8ce5d04ab","tid":2235421,"uid":319228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8448f05349d8989e7a419daef4d51c46c5ac7226","tid":2235421,"uid":186177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T16:41:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://y-brush.com/en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fy-brush.com%2Fen&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr8jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=072b4ba3\" target=\"_blank\">https://y-brush.com/en</a><br />\n樓豬又抄"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:10:33.000Z","msg":"對唔住 係我見識太少<br />\n大家可以出返去先啦"},{"pid":"7950e5ce9d8f2f140dae46f186e4a0b70964f62d","tid":2235421,"uid":254809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:22:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c7eb3157e6c9e6555b59de7445638024e584587","tid":2235421,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89939ada85ab88a5e11cd347bad5e2c8ce5d04ab","tid":2235421,"uid":319228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8448f05349d8989e7a419daef4d51c46c5ac7226","tid":2235421,"uid":186177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T16:41:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://y-brush.com/en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fy-brush.com%2Fen&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZu